original_title: Golf Champion 'Chick' Evans Links with Sweedie
overview: "Chick" Evans, western amateur golf champion, is seen playing golf with his sister. Sweedie is the cook for a family of "get-rich-quicks" and treated very roughly until she receives a letter telling her that her uncle has left her an immense fortune. She is then handled with white gloves. To be a society lady she must wear fine clothes and play golf.
title: Golf Champion 'Chick' Evans Links with Sweedie
